Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:28.91,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠れない夜に　聞いた物語が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:33.67,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絵空事だとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.43,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠を知るより　快楽を求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:54.25,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を悔やんでしまうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:02:00.95,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の深くに　住み着いた影から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.80,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃げるためだとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:10.54,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それでも　あたしはあたしを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:14.15,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛していられるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:18.01,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半分に割れた太陽が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.35,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝を連れてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:25.50,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇に慣れた神経を　じわり刺激する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:30.69,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き忘れたの愛は　あえてそのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:35.56,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シナリオの消えた物語は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:40.83,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由に　自由に　舵をとって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:47.33,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと　高くへ　舞い上がって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:28.91,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無法入眠的夜晚 聽到的那個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:33.67,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是天馬行空的妄想的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.43,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其探求永遠的奧秘 不如把握當下的歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:54.25,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓此時此刻成為一生的悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:02:00.95,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是為了逃避盤踞在內心深處的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.80,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片黑影的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:10.54,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 我還能發自內心地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:14.15,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛著自己的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:18.01,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成兩半的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.35,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來了明媚清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:25.50,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微微刺激著已經習慣黑暗的神經
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:30.69,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把忘了帶走的愛原封不動地擺在那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:35.56,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺了劇本的故事就會..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:40.83,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由地 自由地  操起船舵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:47.33,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起飛向更高的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:28.58,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとつだけ　叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:40.61,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の手の中 揺れる小さな花でいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.43,0:22:47.16,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はじめてみる眩しいこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.58,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君ともしはぐれたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.00,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:05.70,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見つけだして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:23.69,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目覚めたら　そばにいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:31.56,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:28.58,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只能實現一個願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:40.61,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為在你手中隨風搖曳的小花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.43,0:22:47.16,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個陌生 而又炫目的世界裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.58,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕和你走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.00,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:05.70,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:23.69,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來的時候 就在你身邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:31.56,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:58.34,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(980,580)}{\fad(250,150)}#3 「散華..禮彌」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:24:09.50,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,500)}#4 「普通的...女孩子...」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 妳..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.82,0:00:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳是不是有點一拐一拐的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才腳滑的時候扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒事的 至少到家之前還..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等..等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 你在摸哪裡..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回家的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆之間並沒有交談
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後又想要什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時是不是就應該多問問她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後回想起來..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時光..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就是拯救她的最後一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚昧的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳以為我不會察覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓妳踏出這個家門一步了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校也別想去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混球也不准見！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經..忍不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不需要什麼朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種生活..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳只要有我在就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這瓶藥..把一切破壞掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳只要有我在就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊..沒有死成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早上好 禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳打破約定晚上擅自溜出門了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..因為月亮非常之美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以忽然想做個森林浴 想著想著就..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 妳給我小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳的行動對我的評價會有影響啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 少說幾句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以對禮彌這樣說話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親您還沒用完餐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌 昨天真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不該那樣打妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我的錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很感謝父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此 妳能體諒我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌 別忘了能保護得了妳的只有我..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳穿著校服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過妳暫時要在家學習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團一郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌 去換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道些什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 關於昨夜的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們查清了那個少年的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紫陽高中的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是二町目寺廟家的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要對降谷同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為了讓他再也不能接近禮彌..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把他“去勢”了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷同學..有危險了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊 真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把自己做出來的復活藥水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓死去的巴布灌下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腦子到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:07:02.67,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 巴布 快下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你好歹也是寺廟家的兒子 真是的..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:09.67,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩嘛 來嘛巴布~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:14.79,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布醬~看這邊~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說是吧 萌路醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懷疑他的倫理觀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 說的正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然早就知道哥是個會愛上僵屍娘的那種..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡趣味 超級變態的傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然嚴重到這個地步..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 輪不到妳講啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我說不定確實做了一件很可怕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布真的就這樣活過來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就不高興嗎？巴布活過來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛..高興是高興啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是居然真的活過來了..這種事..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳說那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽 那個鼻音超重的獨特叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是貨真價實的巴布啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布~快下來嘛~下來~下來~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:09.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~看這邊 看啊~巴布醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣..它果然還是有點怪怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看它的眼睛還在發光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢..總覺得以前的它更富有感情..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是特徵沒有變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能有什麼事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你想啊 如果真的復活了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它變得像僵屍一樣襲擊人類..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被咬的人也變成僵屍..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事你能保證不會發生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈 怎麼可能發生這種像漫畫情節一樣的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對絕對能保證嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布 巴布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 哥 你的包不要了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了 我今天要翹課
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:08:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥他買了另一只貓來養 結果硬說成他把巴布復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 巴布復活了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈 很好很好 哈哈哈哈..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前沒兩下就肯讓我抓的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 赤手空拳的會不會很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是有晨練嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為姐姐有監督千紘的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是堂姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 居然跑到那裏面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 你要進去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來一杯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就繼續被她擺佈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長 都看不到盡頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等..等我一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦到了..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個洞要通到哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股卡住過不去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然巴布醬也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你也稍微關心我一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽得見對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的..千紘你這個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了出口..咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的下面？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 茂木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1045,160)}一\N之\N伍  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(795,330)}康\N孝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,260)}性\N別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,363)}·
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,420)}帥\N哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡棒球嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？嗯..喜歡看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃..喜歡看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只喜歡看？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這樣你才發育不起來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎這裡嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡舒服嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎這裡嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對茂木毛手毛腳也空虛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟只是個茂木啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 康孝同學 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這話什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找還是得找個散女的大小姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..有事想問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降..降谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊那個..我是問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的降谷千紘同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降...谷...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎？茂木同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..好像今天還沒有來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳..妳找他有什麼事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？不是的..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他..他要被“去勢”了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噶！剛剛..才從大小姐的口中..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去..去..？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳對降谷他啊啊..！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..我沒有說什麼奇怪的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷同學 到底在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你說禮彌在那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用驚動她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去跟著她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不聽我的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？不能理解..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 巴布到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗那傢夥也沒跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼有監督的義務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 快下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃紫陽花的葉子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等..等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡莫非是..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然..是昨天那傢夥逞強爬過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她這個時候會在這..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在那個廢棄的旅館等下去..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能見到他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那裡去的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想因我的緣故..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而給降谷同學添麻煩..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想到哪裡去 禮彌？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林浴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要這樣的話 是不是走得有點遠了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成那就是禮彌的父親嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話還能原諒妳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是個聰明的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳是散華的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的女兒啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在談什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的行為是怎麼回事 禮彌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 的確..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確是你的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算這樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也並不代表連我的內心和身體都屬於你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點就好..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我也擁有一點點的自由！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個自由具體上來說是怎樣的自由？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是單純想要外出的自由嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的自由？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等 父親！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就好 只要今天就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 反正妳是要去見那個叫降谷的男人吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什..什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼冒出來的 這個髒兮兮的貓！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布..醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別靠過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會過敏的..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布醬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧 真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然真的復活了..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！千萬不要碰它！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被弄髒的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成那之後降谷同學把藥完成了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那瓶藥..其實已經完成了..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌 讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷..同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌..？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 應一聲啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然真的死了..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底是多麼開不得玩笑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把我復活吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..還是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷..同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷..同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎..麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有讓妳喝下藥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為..什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團一郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷..同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照約定..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你負起責任哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了你不少關照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.39,0:23:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和寫這個的人見面之後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和他好好地談了談
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 散華禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:23:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的...女孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都要看哦萌路~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著理解了另一個我的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.31,0:24:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不再猶豫了
